       Shrinking Man Installation Instructions
------------------------------------------------------
 1. If you want to override the default installation
    location (/usr/local/), edit src/config.py
    according to your likes.

 2. Run the following command in the root directory
    of this package:
    
      sudo ./install.py
      
    This should work on Systems such as Ubuntu
    Linux. On other Linux distributions, try this
    instead:
    
      su -c "./install.py"

 3. Finished. To run the application, type this
    command:

      shrinkingman
